17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 5-400 of Title 2, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. Notwithstanding any other provision of law, no person, firm,
22 association, corporation, or any other entity of this state shall
23 manufacture, compound, brew, distill, produce, process, sell,
24 deliver, distribute, hold, offer, or expose for sale any of the
